TITLE: Creating and Styling SFSymbol Image in SwiftUI - Swift
DESCRIPTION: Creates a SwiftUI Image view using an SFSymbol system name. It demonstrates conditional rendering of symbols based on a boolean state variable and applies font modifiers to control the size and weight of the symbol.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ivanvorobei/swiftui/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: Swift
