TITLE: Declaring State Variable in SwiftUI View - Swift
DESCRIPTION: Declares a private variable within a SwiftUI View struct using the `@State` property wrapper. This makes the variable a local source of truth, and any changes to its value will automatically trigger a view update.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ivanvorobei/swiftui/blob/master/README.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: Swift
CODE:
```
@State var show = false
```

